OcarinaSong
Plugin for Bukkit

Allows players to use a LoZ-Style Ocarina by right clicking with an Ocarina (Brick), and then tapping Up/Down/Left/Right/Sneak 
to play notes in the exact same fashion as LoZ

+All the classic LoZ songs will be playable on it

(In the list so far: Song of Time, Song of Storms, Song of Healing)

To Do:
-Add more songs/permissions



Permission Nodes:
jack.ocarina - Allows user to play Ocarina
jack.ocarina.time - Allows user to change time via Song of Time
jack.ocarina.storms - Allows user to change weather via Song of Storms
jack.ocarina.healing - Allows user to change weather via Song of Storms